Nico Smith is a collage artist whose work centers on the transformation of found materials into layered visual narratives. Using paper, texture, and mixed media, they reimagine fragments of everyday life into evocative compositions that explore memory, identity, and the passage of time.

Each piece is an invitation to look closer to find meaning in the unexpected and beauty in the broken. Through intuitive process and thoughtful assembly, Nico Smith constructs artworks that challenge perception and invite personal interpretation.
Collage in motion animates cutouts and textures to create dynamic, evolving narratives. It blends film, animation, and traditional collage, bringing static images to life through movement and rhythm.
